              <br /><br />
              The controller is the natural person or legal entity that single-handedly
              or jointly with others makes decisions as to the purposes of and resources
              for the processing of personal data (e.g., names, e-mail addresses,
              etc.).
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-3">
            <h1 class="font-display text-lg lg:text-xl text-black">
              Storage duration
            </h1>
