            and processed by me for the purpose of processing your request. I do
            not pass these data on without your consent.
            <br /><br />
            These data are processed on the basis of Art. 6(1)(b) GDPR if your inquiry
            is related to the fulfillment of a contract or is required for the performance
            of pre-contractual measures. In all other cases, the data are processed
            on the basis of my legitimate interest in the effective handling of inquiries
            submitted to me (Art. 6(1)(f) GDPR) or on the basis of your consent (Art.
            6(1)(a) GDPR) if it has been obtained; the consent can be revoked at
            any time.
            <br /><br />
            The data sent by you to me via contact requests remain with me until
            you request me to delete, revoke your consent to the storage or the purpose
            for the data storage lapses (e.g. after completion of your request).
            Mandatory statutory provisions - in particular statutory retention periods
